profile:
Magnolia Construction prides itself on the ability to listen and anticipate wants and needs. That’s what makes us exceptional at customizing our services to the unique situation of each and every client. We guide your vision through the entire renovation process and ensure that we are on the same page as to the best way to achieve it.

Our team of designers and builders brings expertise in a wide variety of aspects in home remodelling, and our track record of customer satisfaction earns us repeat business and referrals. You’ll find us as attentive and courteous in customer service as in the remodelling work itself.

We’ve transformed many a kitchen in Ottawa, with renovations ranging from islands and new counter tops to knocking down walls and changing the entire dynamic to a more contemporary space. Our extensive experience in kitchen renovations means you’re getting highly skilled craftsmanship to execute an exquisite transformation. Our clients give us rave reviews and have great things to say about the renovations we’ve done for the kitchens and other living spaces.

Our bathroom renovations deliver quality results, on time and on budget. We’ll work with you to create an upgraded bathroom that makes you want to linger for a while, light a candle and relax. We’ve remodeled countless bathrooms in Ottawa homes, from counters and sinks to showers & tubs to tile floors. We leave no stone unturned when we executive a renovation, keeping your full satisfaction in mind at every measurement, cut and fitting.

Magnolia will transform your basement from “blah” to “wow.” We’ll work with you to design and deliver a functional, livable basement space that your family (or your tenant) will truly enjoy. We have a knack for translating visions into reality. Talk to Magnolia about how we can work together to build a dream basement. When it comes to basements there’s no need to aim low. You deserve the best quality renovation. Magnolia can make that happen.
services: Bathroom renovations, kitchen renovations, basement renovations, additions, general contracting, landscaping, decks
name: Magnolia Construction

profile:
With 15 years of experience behind us, Pro-Valley Renovations has worked with many clients on a great variety of home renovations projects.

What makes us unique is that we've had many of the same clients return to us over and over again in those 15 years for new home renovation needs, whether it be to add to their existing house or for a different house. We also have to thank our clients for their wonderful referrals over the years as that is a true statement of their satisfaction with Pro-Valley Renovations' work.

Pro-Valley Renovations difference is listening to clients and having the experience behind us to meet any home renovation need and deliver a quality project, on budget and on time. Whether it be your new kitchen, bathroom, exterior or other home renovations, Pro-Valley Renovations is ready to listen and help make your project one that just might make you one of our returning clients too.

Check out our website or call us directly at 613-327-3255 today.

profile:
We are located in Ottawa, Ontario Canada.
Our commitment is to work with you by accomplishing step by step what you need and want when it comes to your organizational space, ensuring at the same time, you get the most out of your buck. We do this by working with you every step of the way.

From the first phone call to the final installation, we want you to have an enjoyable experience with remarkable results when it comes to obtaining the organization you desire.

Starting with a thorough understanding of your needs, we will design a custom solution using Chief Architect software to design the best solution to your organizational space. The Chief Architect automated building tools make home design, remodeling, interior design, and kitchen & bath design easy. Using this program, we at the Cabinet Workshop model give our customers a high degree of personalization. You can personalize your organizational space to suit your needs and adapt it to your decor with limitless possibilities of styles, finishes, colours, modular layouts and sizes. Because the design process takes time and expertise, there is a fee a associated with the service. However, because we want your service, this fee is automatically waved when you hire us to take care of your organizational needs. From the very start, we want you to be happy and we do that by saving you money while at the same time, providing you professional organizational solutions to your home.

When it comes time to install, your schedule and preferences are our primary consideration. Our installers are expert at their craft and will treat your home like their own, leaving it cleaner and neater than when they arrived.
name: Cabinet Workshop
